<br>
I was fighting in Blackburrow, when a level 54 mage wandered in and started casting Lava Shield on everyone.  My lucky day <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :) --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/smile.gif ALT=":)"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END--> <br>
<br>
Well, with that I ran off to train multiple gnolls on myself.  It worked, and I watched in glee as each gnoll was burned for 25 points of damage when they hit me.  My hp was going down as well, but I wasn't worried; there was only a burly gnoll left.  Well, it hit me several times, got burned several times, and kept at it.  Suddenly, I fell to the ground, unconscious.  I was bleeding to death!!!  I was down to about one bubble in the purple, when that gnoll bashed me for one point of damage.  <br>
<br>
A burly gnoll bashes YOU for 1 point of damage!<br>
You have slain a burly gnoll!<br>
You gain experience!<br>
<br>
Needless to say, that was the first time I ever slew a beast while it was unconscious <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :) --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/smile.gif ALT=":)"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END--> <br>
