<br>
I can't remember if it was a multiple pull or what, but our fight got nasty, and we both ended up running for the zone with a pixel or so of health left. We had both been poisoned in the course of the fight, so the first thing that happened was both us being knocked unconscious right after zoning... then watching our health slowly tick away as the poison worked.<br>
<br>
Then, with less than a purple bubble left, his poison broke and he regained consciousness and I followed him back to the land of the living soon after. <br>
