<!--EZCODE AUTOLINK START--><a href="http://www.jibnet.net">www.jibnet.net</a><!--EZCODE AUTOLINK END--> <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#3B3B3B><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub13.ezboard.com/uprenn.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Prenn</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br> <font color=#FF0000>(1/17/01 4:50:36 pm)</font><br>    <BR><img src=http://www.geocities.com/adhfsdfhad/portrait2.JPG WIDTH=60 HEIGHT=60></td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: The closest I've been to death without dying </span><hr size=1> I don't think anyone can beat this for 'close' value...<br>
<br>
I was lvl36, grouped with a lvl35 rogue. We were killing clockworks, the foreman, and the pred in sol a. I tanked 100% of the time because of my ability to heal myself, and evade. I did all of the pulling, of course.<br>
<br>
Eventually I decided to check on the goblin bartender, since when we met I had been soloing the bar area (it's great for 1 person, but it doesn't support two people 35+)<br>
<br>
I ran in, and the bartender wasn't up. But the drunkard was. He was green, and his common drop is *very* nice, so I decided 'What the hell?' and pulled him from his spawn point, to the secret hallway behind the foreman.<br>
<br>
Anyone who knows sol a knows that there's about 15 goblins between the two places :)<br>
<br>
I ended up at 1 bubble when the pull was over. My partner said that he would tank it while I bandaged up, since the drunkard was green to both of us.<br>
<br>
His pet, his 150+ dmg nukes, and his 15pt dmg shield made us realize the errors of our ways. I called for us to zone, but it took too long for us to get going.<br>
<br>
We burst through the secret wall, 5 seconds from the zone.<br>
<br>
A young goblin backstabs YOU for 110 points of dmg<br>
A fire goblin hits YOU for 63 points of dmg.<br>
You are unconcious!<br>
<br>
At this point, I stared down at my body in shock, unable to believe that I was about to die.<br>
<br>
Suddenly, the drunkard+pet, and the 3 goblins in the room LEFT ME ALONE! In about 1 second, I regenned a single hp and feigned.<br>
<br>
Unfortunately, when the goblins decided to leave me alone, they went for my partner and cut him down 2 seconds from the solb zone.<br>
<br>
I honestly don't know why they went after him instead of killing me, since when you get really low on hp, even lvl1 mobs will aggro on you.<br>
<br>
He got a lvl56 rez, though :)<br>
<br>
For anyone who knows the drunkard's common drop (which he had, since he wasn't wielding the staff), you will understand the irony of what happened. :( <p><font size="2"><font color="ashen"><center>
Pren, lvl40 Human Monk on The Tribunal server</font>
